# 🌍 World Time Checker

> **Farcaster Mini App for tracking world time zones with beautiful pixel art design**

[![Live Demo](https://img.shields.io/badge/Live-Demo-orange?style=for-the-badge)](https://terra-pacing-05021987.figma.site)
[![Farcaster](https://img.shields.io/badge/Farcaster-Mini_App-purple?style=for-the-badge)](https://www.farcaster.xyz/)
[![React](https://img.shields.io/badge/React-18.2-blue?style=for-the-badge&logo=react)](https://reactjs.org/)
[![TypeScript](https://img.shields.io/badge/TypeScript-5.3-blue?style=for-the-badge&logo=typescript)](https://www.typescriptlang.org/)
[![Tailwind CSS](https://img.shields.io/badge/Tailwind-v4.0-06B6D4?style=for-the-badge&logo=tailwindcss)](https://tailwindcss.com/)

## ✨ Features

- **🕐 Live World Clocks** - Real-time timezone tracking across the globe
- **🎨 Pixel Art Design** - Beautiful retro-inspired globe character
- **📱 Mobile-First** - Optimized for mobile Farcaster experience
- **🌍 URL Sharing** - Share specific timezone configurations
- **💾 Auto-Save** - Local storage with Supabase backup
- **🎮 Haptic Feedback** - Enhanced mobile interaction
- **🔗 Deep Linking** - Direct timezone setup via URL parameters
- **⚡ Offline Support** - Works without internet connection

## 🚀 Quick Start

### Prerequisites

- Node.js 18+ 
- npm/yarn/pnpm
- Supabase account (optional for backend features)

### Installation

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/world-time-checker.git
cd world-time-checker

# Install dependencies
npm install

# Set up environment variables
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env with your Supabase credentials

# Start development server
npm run dev
```

### Build for Production

```bash
# Build the app
npm run build

# Preview production build
npm run preview
```

## 🛠 Tech Stack

- **Frontend**: React 18 + TypeScript
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS v4 + Custom Brand System
- **UI Components**: shadcn/ui
- **Backend**: Supabase (Database + Auth + Storage)
- **Integration**: Farcaster Mini App SDK
- **Build Tool**: Vite
- **State Management**: React Hooks + Local Storage

## 📦 Project Structure

```
├── App.tsx                 # Main application component
├── components/             # React components
│   ├── ui/                # shadcn/ui components
│   ├── PixelGlobeIcon.tsx # Custom pixel art globe
│   ├── TimezoneSelector.tsx
│   └── WorldClock.tsx
├── hooks/                 # Custom React hooks
├── services/              # API and business logic
├── styles/                # Global CSS and themes
├── supabase/              # Backend functions
└── utils/                 # Utility functions
```

## 🌐 Environment Variables

```bash
