## 🎯 URL Parameters

The app supports deep linking with timezone parameters:

```
https://yourapp.com/?tz1=Asia/Seoul&tz2=America/New_York&tz3=Europe/London
```

## 🎨 Brand Colors

The app uses a warm orange brand color system:

- **Primary**: `#FFB74D` (Orange 500)
- **Accent**: `#FF9800` (Orange 600) 
- **Text**: `#E65100` (Orange 800)
- **Background**: Gradient from orange to yellow

## 🚀 Deployment

### Vercel (Recommended)

```bash
# Install Vercel CLI
npm i -g vercel

# Deploy
vercel
```

### Netlify

```bash
# Build
npm run build

# Deploy dist/ folder to Netlify
```

### Manual Deployment

The app builds to a static `dist/` folder that can be deployed to any static hosting service.

